From b842f5e3be3052142d8dd419145a8be42c1785e6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Martin=20Storsj=C3=B6?= <martin@martin.st>
Date: Thu, 13 Mar 2025 14:14:02 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 03/24] crt: Redirect long double funcs to double, if long
 double == double

These cases are files only used for x86; the corresponding cases on
arm/aarch64 are implemented in separate files (or used from the CRT).
---
 mingw-w64-crt/math/cbrtl.c          | 8 ++++++++
 mingw-w64-crt/math/hypotl.c         | 4 ++++
 mingw-w64-crt/math/modfl.c          | 4 ++++
 mingw-w64-crt/math/sqrtl.c          | 8 ++++++++
